492
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,980
that I fell asleep on the roadside.

493
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:48,500
When I woke up,

494
00:26:48,580 --> 00:26:50,420
I saw my master and my senior sister.

495
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:52,620
So I followed them.

496
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:55,380
I learned martial arts and became a soldier to protect my country.

497
00:26:55,980 --> 00:26:57,220
I enjoy it so much!

498
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:01,940
Do you still hate him?

499
00:27:02,580 --> 00:27:03,220
Who?

500
00:27:03,780 --> 00:27:04,740
Your father.

501
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:07,100
I don't even care about him now.

502
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:09,020
He doesn't deserve my hatred.

503
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:10,020
I am

504
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:11,540
General Feng who

505
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:12,460
intimidates people now.

506
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:14,660
All I care about

507
00:27:14,780 --> 00:27:16,380
is the citizens of the Western State.

508
00:27:17,580 --> 00:27:19,140
Looks like you are

509
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:21,460
much more open-minded than I am.

510
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:22,420
You monks

511
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:24,340
believe in helping everyone, right?

512
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:25,820
Since you care about everyone,

513
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:27,620
what's the big deal if you hate the Emperor of Nanxiao?

514
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:30,300
That's true.

515
00:27:31,540 --> 00:27:32,940
You are right.

516
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:01,740
Greetings, Mr. Huan.

517
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:07,340
Is this gentleman your friend?

518
00:28:11,860 --> 00:28:12,820
My best friend.

519
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:23,460
Are you a couple?

520
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:28,220
No.

521
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:30,700
Then, are you

522
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:32,220
engaged, Miss?

523
00:28:35,900 --> 00:28:36,620
I'm not.

524
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:41,900
My last name is Houmochen

525
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:43,180
and my given name is Yue.

526
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:46,300
Nice to meet you, Mr. Houmochen.

527
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:48,820
I'm…

528
00:28:49,540 --> 00:28:50,820
Would I give away

529
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:52,460
my identity if I tell him my last name is Cui?

530
00:28:57,220 --> 00:28:59,180
This lady is from the Nanchen Royal Mansion

531
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,640
in the Western State.

532
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:03,940
You mean the junior Prince of Nanchen's Mansion?

533
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:06,340
Yes.

534
00:29:07,660 --> 00:29:08,740
It's such a pleasure to meet you!

535
00:29:09,980 --> 00:29:10,980
I have some fine wine

536
00:29:11,100 --> 00:29:12,780
that's over one hundred years old.

537
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,100
May I have the honor

538
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:16,140
to have a drink with you, Miss?

539
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:18,780
Since you have some fine wine,

540
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,500
why don't you share it

541
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:21,740
with all of us?

542
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,940
That's right, Mr. Houmochen.

543
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:29,260
Drinking fine wine alone is such a waste.

544
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:30,900
It'd be more fun to drink it with other people.

545
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:32,380
That's right. Mr. Houmochen,

546
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,380
don't hide it.

547
00:29:33,500 --> 00:29:34,980
Share it with all of us!

548
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:36,420
