-Share it!

549
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:38,580
Alright, fine. I'll share it with you lot!

550
00:29:38,740 --> 00:29:40,460
You greedy drinkers.

551
00:29:48,580 --> 00:29:49,260
Thank you!

552
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:53,500
You are not afraid of giving your identity away?

553
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:55,700
We'll be leaving tomorrow.

554
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:56,860
It's okay.

555
00:29:59,700 --> 00:30:01,260
I wonder if you

556
00:30:01,660 --> 00:30:02,500
protect every disciple

557
00:30:02,620 --> 00:30:03,900
of yours like this.

558
00:30:07,100 --> 00:30:07,700
Of course.

559
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:15,040
During the reign of Taishi,

560
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:19,260
the people lived a happy life.

561
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:23,620
Ever since my dear left me,

562
00:30:25,180 --> 00:30:27,860
I've missed him day and night.

