00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:34,340
I've missed him day and night.

565
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:36,540
This is a folk song of the South.

566
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:38,140
The Qin master likes it,

567
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:39,260
so he plays it quite often.

568
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,380
But you don't

569
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:42,660
put too much thought into it.

570
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:44,420
Why not?

571
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,420
Ask him.

572
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,180
He asked me

573
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:49,740
the same question in the past.

574
00:30:53,850 --> 00:30:55,130
"Ziye Songs of the Four Seasons"

575
00:30:55,290 --> 00:30:56,640
is also known as "Ziye Songs of Wu".

576
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:59,390
The lady who wrote the songs was named Ziye.

577
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:05,140
Huan Yu.

578
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:06,440
Let the Qin master

579
00:31:06,560 --> 00:31:07,920
play something elegant.

580
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:17,120
What's wrong

581
00:31:17,560 --> 00:31:18,840
with Ziye Songs of Wu?

582
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:25,360
You are quite busy today.

583
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,400
People like to take a boat ride

584
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:27,920
when the weather is nice.

585
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:29,200
Mr. Huan.

586
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,240
-Mr. Huan.
-Mr. Huan.

587
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,440
You guys go ahead.

588
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,600
I got a carriage.

589
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:37,680
I'll wait for you on the other end.

590
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,760
Mr. Huan, you are not coming with us?

591
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,520
I…

592
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:42,600
I'm afraid of water.

593
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:44,800
Afraid of water?

594
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:47,960
Come on! Just go!

595
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:49,400
I'll wait for you in the south of the town.

596
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:52,400
Here. Be careful.

597
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,240
Mr. Huan.

598
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:07,280
You love taking a boat tour.

599
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:08,880
Why don't you go with them?

600
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:11,280
I don't want

601
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,760
to be a third wheel.

602
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:33,120
Today is the Double Ninth Festival.

603
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:34,120
Yes.

604
00:32:34,990 --> 00:32:36,800
We are supposed to climb a mountain,

605
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,840
but we are taking a boat instead.

606
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:40,920
We'll climb a mountain

607
00:32:41,190 --> 00:32:42,120
when we go back tonight.

608
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,480
That's true.

609
00:33:02,040 --> 00:33:03,080
I'm sorry!

610
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,400
The paddle slipped.

611
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,000
Please sit tight.

612
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:10,280
♫Like a gust of wind gently brushing♫

613
00:33:12,530 --> 00:33:16,420
♫Like a cloud waiting for the rain to fall♫

614
00:33:19,090 --> 00:33:21,420
♫There is a corner in my heart♫

615
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:24,680
♫Where my expectation is glowing♫

616
00:33:25,110 --> 00:33:30,040
♫It's the shooting star lighting up the night sky for you♫

617
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:28,080
Why don't you

618
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:29,400
like the Ziye Songs of Wu?

619
00:33:31,920 --> 00:33:33,520
You stopped the Qin Master just now.

620
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:34,400
Why is that?

621
00:33:35,140 --> 00:33:39,880
♫There are so many wishes I want to say to you♫

622
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:38,840
I'll head out to enjoy the scenery.

623
00:33:41,610 --> 00:33:46,260
♫There is still a hidden sore of longing♫

624
00:33:48,430 --> 00:33:51,270
♫My thoughts stained three feet of white snow♫

625
00:33:51,590 --> 00:33:54,600
♫Counting the days for your return over and over again♫

626
00:33:54,600 --> 00:34:00,550
♫Flowers blossom and flowers fall, my heart only clings for you♫

627
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:04,070
♫My obsession is silent♫

628
00:34:04,719 --> 00:34:07,480
♫I use all my life to guard only one person♫

629
00:34:07,679 --> 00:34:13,480
♫I say nothing, only hoping to spend my life with you♫

630
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,159
Young master,

631
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,320
the large ship ahead

632
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,239
is quite famous

633
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,719
in Jiangling.

634
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,760
It docks here often.

635
00:34:14,170 --> 00:34:17,060
♫I'm full of love for you♫

636
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,760
The ladies of the rich families

637
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,639
often get together on the ship.

638
00:34:17,850 --> 00:34:20,960
♫Waiting to unlock the years of time♫

639
00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:21,320
This young master on the awning boat,

640
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:26,719
♫Our eyes will still be full of stars when we reunite♫

641
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,880
are you an out-of-towner?

642
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:26,120
Yes. He's an important guest of Longkang Academy!

643
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,120
Have the young master come on our ship.

644
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,360
My Lady said that any important guest

645
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,920
of Longkang Academy is considered

646
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:34,560
a distinguished guest of Jiangling!

647
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:38,600
♫Renewing our relationship♫

648
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:35,639
If you don't mind,

649
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,920
please get on our ship!

650
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:38,280
Today is the Double Ninth Festival!

651
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,480
She'd like to treat you to some Fortune Wine.

652
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:45,040
♫We used to be inseparable♫

653
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:43,040
Thank you. Maybe some other time.

654
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:49,900
♫Heartfelt thoughts are written on a piece of paper♫

655
00:34:49,520 --> 00:34:50,760
You are appreciating the scenery, right?

656
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:53,250
♫Thoughts to you overflow out from the window♫

657
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:51,520
I'll join you.

658
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,200
Miss,

659
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:55,040
if you were one second later,

660
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:59,520
♫Who shall see through the deep sorrow on the paper♫

661
00:34:55,160 --> 00:34:55,800
your husband

662
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,880
would be dragged on the ship for a drink.

663
00:34:59,770 --> 00:35:03,280
♫My obsession is silent♫

664
00:35:03,080 --> 00:35:04,360
What's Fortune Wine?

665
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:06,640
♫I use all my life to guard only one person♫

666
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:06,600
They call it Chrysanthemum Wine

667
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,520
in the south.

668
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:12,330
♫I say nothing, only hoping to spend my life with you♫

669
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:13,440
Boatman.

670
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:16,240
♫I'm full of love for you♫

671
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,160
Yes.

672
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,720
Where can I buy some authentic Chrysanthemum Wine?

673
00:35:16,120 --> 00:35:16,840
It's not far from here.

674
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:20,720
♫Waiting to unlock the years of time♫

675
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:18,840
When we get to the shore, I'll show you.

676
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:27,620
♫Our eyes will still be full of stars when we reunite♫

677
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:33,910
♫We will still promise with each other when we reunite♫

678
00:35:40,790 --> 00:35:41,520
Two bottles of Chrysanthemum Wine, please.

679
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:43,960
Here, your wine.

680
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:44,440
Okay.

681
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,560
And one more.

682
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:46,200
Thank you.

683
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:46,720
Take care.

684
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:51,080
Have a taste.

685
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,360
Miss,

686
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,400
would you like a cornelian cherry pouch?

687
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:08,880
Pick one. It can ward off evil spirits.

688
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:10,680
Yes. It can ward off evil spirits.

689
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,640
Take a look.

690
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,360
Why don't you pick one too?

691
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,040
It's for ladies,

692
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:22,560
not for men.

693
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,200
Then what can he do to ward off evil spirits?

694
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:26,600
He can drink the Chrysanthemum Wine.

695
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,480
We'll have this one.

696
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,120
Oh, no!

697
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,600
Three coins. Only three coins.

698
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,520
We came from the North.

699
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,640
We don't have any local money.

700
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,480
This is all we have.

701
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:40,160
But,

702
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:42,560
it's too much! Too much!

703
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:44,000
Please take it.

704
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,280
You can go home

705
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,920
and enjoy the festival with this money.

706
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:49,800
Thank you!

707
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,000
Thank you so much!

708
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:10,200
Master, drink some more.

709
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:11,400
The ma'am said

710
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:12,320
it'd help ward off evil spirits.

711
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:37,920
Do you want some more?

712
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:40,520
Yes.

713
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:44,040
Drink mine then.

714
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,520
What about you?

715
00:37:49,210 --> 00:37:49,960
I'll go buy another bottle.

716
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,200
Okay. Since it's Fortune Wine,

717
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,840
the more, the better.

718
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:09,540
[Longkang Academy]

719
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:16,400
Miss, you had Fortune Wine?

720
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:20,840
You can smell it?

721
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,160
Does it smell bad?

722
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,640
No. Chrysanthemum Wine smells very good.

723
00:38:26,200 --> 00:38:28,000
His Highness will have a chat with my master.

724
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:29,400
He'll be back later.

725
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,720
I brewed some tea for you.

726
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,120
Please enjoy it, Miss.

727
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,000
Thank you!

728
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,480
You are welcome!

729
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,200
Hold on.

730
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,040
Have you ever heard

731
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:43,400
of "Ziye Songs of the Four Seasons"?

732
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:44,960
"Ziye Songs of Wu"?

733
00:38:45,120 --> 00:38:45,640
Yes.

734
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,800
Why did my master take you to listen to that?

735
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,320
Is there something wrong with the song?

736
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,640
Some are okay.

737
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:55,400
But some of them have inappropriate lyrics,

738
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:58,640
like "Clean sheet is put on my bed,

739
00:38:59,150 --> 00:39:02,680
inviting my beloved to come to my room.”

740
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,320
That wouldn't be proper for you.

741
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:08,640
I'll go back to work now.

742
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,680
Please take a rest.

743
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,520
“Clean sheet is put on my bed,

744
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:17,680
inviting my beloved to come to my room.”

745
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,400
That is improper!

746
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:27,320
Miss, we have a guest

747
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,320
who wants to see you.

748
00:39:35,640 --> 00:39:36,440
I, Houmochen Yue,

749
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:37,680
didn't know who you were earlier

750
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,480
and offended you. I'm here to apologize to you.

751
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:42,680
You did nothing wrong.

752
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:43,760
Why do you apologize?

753
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:46,920
Because I didn't know who you were.

754
00:39:47,300 --> 00:39:48,120
While having food at home,

755
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:49,440
my parents mentioned

756
00:39:49,810 --> 00:39:50,880
that a guest from the Cui family presented

757
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:51,880
800 volumes of books to Nanxiao.

758
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:54,000
Only then did I suddenly realize who you are.

759
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:55,680
My identity is not important,

760
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:56,920
and you don't have

761
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,240
to apologize for that.

762
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,760
Houmochen Yue,

763
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,040
you certainly need to apologize.

764
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:04,560
Not only that,

765
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,320
you also need to thank me for stopping you

766
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,120
from flirting with her.

767
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,720
Otherwise, you'd be in big trouble.

768
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:11,680
Neither His Majesty

769
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:13,280
nor her master,

770
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:14,600
the junior Prince of Nanchen,

771
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:15,960
would forgive you!

772
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:18,480
Thank you for that, Mr. Huan!

773
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,600
It's okay.

774
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,640
Miss Cui is not a petty person.

775
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,080
Just relax

776
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,160
and leave.

777
00:40:29,200 --> 00:40:31,240
What? You have more to say?

778
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,360
Miss, I'm aware that you are

779
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,640
out of my league,

780
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,080
but I still wanna know

781
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:40,720
if you are engaged with someone.

782
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:49,200
You still won't give up?

783
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,920
You are asking me this

784
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,480
because my last name is Cui.

785
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:02,040
Since you ask me to tell you the truth,

786
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,560
you also need to be honest with me.

787
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:05,360
Yes. The Houmochen family

788
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,960
enjoys high prestige as well.

789
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,600
If I can marry a lady from the Cui family…

790
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:09,760
Houmochen Yue,

791
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,960
I advise you to sober up.

792
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,320
Miss Cui is the daughter of

793
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,320
the head of Wushui.

794
00:41:15,680 --> 00:41:18,000
If she were to get married, the six clans would be her first choice.

795
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:19,240
The Liu royal family

796
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,840
and the Beichen aristocratic family would be her second choices.

797
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,560
She's way out of your league.

798
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:24,000
I'm asking Miss Cui here.

799
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,880
Whether you are engaged or not,

800
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:29,520
I just want an answer from you.

801
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,480
I'm not engaged with anyone.

802
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:37,600
But I already

803
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,640
have someone in my heart.

804
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,000
And I won't

805
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:54,120
change my mind.
